,Not Recommended,566990,29192006,Posted: 11 January,all,ToxicTromeo,"First and foremost - this game can be found for free online and played in your browser.  Russian Car Driver is a very clunky game that's hard to recommend.  If you're looking for something to roam the Russian countryside in and run over bears or deer then it might be up your alley.  But if you're looking for any sort of legitimate, fun racing experience then this isn't the game for you.Your car controls more akin to a tank than a car.  The graphics are more reminiscent of the early 2000's/late 90's.  If you play in English then expect a lot of broken English that makes some wording a bit weird.The game does have some okay music, though.  And I guess you learn a fair amount about the history of the Russian automobile industry.This game could be worse - but it can also be a lot, lot better.  Even with some polishing it could potentially turn out at least okay - there are definitely some features in there that could work.  But right now I can't recommend people dropping their money on it.If you're interested in seeing how it actually plays (with some horrible commentary):https://youtu.be/YRxSkPaPHQs"
